<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0760c09shiPuJi"><lb
ed="T" n="0760c09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000056485">京師興唐寺</placeName><persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>傳</head><anchor n="T.50.2061.0760c09"/><p><lb
ed="T" n="0760c10"/><persName key="A009319">釋普寂</persName>，姓<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>憑</sic><corr>馮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz9"/>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005197">蒲州河東</placeName>人也。年纔稚弱，率<lb
ed="T" n="0760c11"/>性軒昂，離俗升壇，循于經律。臨文揣義，逈<lb
ed="T" n="0760c12"/>異恒流。初聞<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000027023">荊州玉泉寺</placeName>，<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>乃往師<lb
ed="T" n="0760c13"/>事，凡六年。<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>奇<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>，盡以<ref type="person" target="#A009582">其</ref>道授焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0700-05-31" key="j19768801977143" notAfter-iso="+0701-02-18">久視<lb
ed="T" n="0760c14"/>中</date>，<persName key="A002099">則天</persName>召<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>至<placeName key="PL000000023581">東都</placeName>論道，因薦<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，乃度<lb
ed="T" n="0760c15"/>為僧。及<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>之卒，天下好釋氏者，咸師事<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0760c16"/><persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>聞<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>高年，特下制令<persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>代<ref type="person" target="#A009582">本師</ref><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/>統<lb
ed="T" n="0760c17"/>其法眾<ptr target="#n1380"/>。<date from-iso="+0735-02-02" key="j19895451989927" to-iso="+0736-02-19">開元<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz10"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>二十三</sic><corr>十三</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz10"/>年</date>，勅<persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023581">都城</ref>居<lb
ed="T" n="0760c18"/>止<ptr target="#n1381"/>。時王公大人競來<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz11"/>謁，<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>嚴重少言，來者<lb
ed="T" n="0760c19"/>難見其和悅之容，遠近尤以此重<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>。<date from-iso="+0739-02-17" key="j19910211991374" to-iso="+0740-02-05">二十七<lb
ed="T" n="0760c20"/>年</date>，終于<placeName key="PL000000056485">上都興唐寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1382"/>。年八十九。時都城士庶<lb
ed="T" n="0760c21"/>謁者皆制弟<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz12"/>子<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz12"/>之服。有制賜諡曰<persName key="A009319">大<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>慧</sic><corr>照</corr></choice>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0760c22"/>師</persName><ptr target="#n1383"/>。及葬，<placeName key="PL000000023580">河南</placeName>尹<persName key="A009351">裴寬</persName>及其妻子，並縗麻列于<lb
ed="T" n="0760c23"/>門徒之次<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1422"/>。傾城哭送，閭里為之空焉。<persName key="A009351">裴<roleName>尹</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760c24"/>之重<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1435"/>職有由矣。<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>之闡化，神異頗多，<persName key="A009351">裴</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760c25"/>皆目擊，又得心印<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1434"/>，歸向越深，時多譏誚。<persName key="A009351">裴</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760c26"/>日夕造謁，執弟子禮曾無差脫。一日詣<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0760c27"/><persName key="A009319">寂</persName>懸知弟子<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>之亡。及<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>之終滅，<persName key="A009351">裴</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0760c28"/>悲慟若喪所親，縗絰徒步出城，妻子同爾，<lb
ed="T" n="0760c29"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1436"/>搢紳之譏生於是矣。</p><pb ed="T" n="0761a" xml:id="T50.2061.0761a"/>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0761a01"/>系曰：人之情也有愛、惡焉，愛之者不見可<lb
ed="T" n="0761a02"/>惡，惡之者不見可愛矣。夫萬物紛綸，任其<lb
ed="T" n="0761a03"/>愛惡，折中之道，可愛而不可惡。愛之者君<lb
ed="T" n="0761a04"/>子也，惡之者小人也，愛之不以道，則君子<lb
ed="T" n="0761a05"/>之病矣。<persName key="A009351">裴<roleName>尹</roleName></persName>冠裳在御，職事在躬，不避密<lb
ed="T" n="0761a06"/>行，顯掇時謗，宜哉。譬諸僧耽俗務，胡不<lb
ed="T" n="0761a07"/>捨袈裟而衣逢掖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g868"/>乎？若實得道，後終期脫<lb
ed="T" n="0761a08"/>屣<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g356"/>，有何不可<anchor xml:id="beg0761001"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0761001"/>？寬不抽簪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1437"/>，何悖禮於<persName key="A002174">丘</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0761a09"/>之門歟？寬若行方外之道，復何誅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1438"/>焉。達人<lb
ed="T" n="0761a10"/>大觀，物無不可矣。</p>
